Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}來做下自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.91,0:00:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我叫…曉美…炎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}還請…多多…關照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美同學因為心臟的疾病一直在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}回到了久違的學校 也會有很多不知所措的事吧
