Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美同學原來在哪裡的學校上學？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}有參加過社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}運動型？ 文藝型？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好長的頭髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}每天早上編起來很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個 我…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}要去保健室才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}知道在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那我來給你帶路吧 我是負責保健的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}大家抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美同學休息時間必須要去保健室吃藥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}啊 這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.26,0:01:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}抱歉啦 纏住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美同學 回頭見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}抱歉啦 大家都沒有惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為轉學生很稀奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}都有些興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不…那個 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不用那麼緊張啦 都是同學嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我是鹿目圓 叫我小圓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以我也叫你小炎可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我…那個 沒怎麼被叫過名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}而且名字也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒有那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好像有種燃燒起來的感覺 我覺得很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}其實名不副實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那樣太可惜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}難得有個帥氣的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎也變得帥氣就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那麼 來解下這個問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你好像一直在休學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}去向朋友借筆記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只是準備體操就貧血了很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}半年中一直睡著 沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎也變得帥氣就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}做不到的 我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只會給人添麻煩 讓自己丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我以後也會一直這樣下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那不如乾脆死掉更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}死掉更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}對 死掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}死掉…的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這…這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}什麼 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}千鈞一髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}已經不要緊了 小炎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}她們是魔法少女 狩獵魔女之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}突然就暴露秘密了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}對班上的同學們要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}鹿目同學 總是跟那種東西戰鬥著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯…要說總是的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那麻美姐倒是老手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我上週才剛剛跟丘比結下契約
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是今天的戰鬥方式比以前要好多了哦 鹿目同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不會…害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}也不是不要緊 雖然也會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:05:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}打倒魔女的話 就會有許多人因此得救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}有去做的價值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}{\pos(217,326)\fs16\b1}walpurgisnacht
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}鹿目同學要在魔女之夜到來之前努力到能獨當一面才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那我要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼 巴學姐明明都死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以才要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為能阻止魔女之夜的就只有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不行的 一個人跟那種東西戰鬥贏不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}連鹿目同學也會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}就算那樣我也是魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}必須要保護大家才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}喂 我們逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為 這是沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}誰都不會恨鹿目同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:06:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎 我很高興能跟你成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}在你被魔女襲擊的時候能趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}現在也為那而感到自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以我覺得能成為魔法少女真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}鹿目同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}再見了 小炎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不要 不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}鹿目同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}明明知道會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}比起救我這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我明明更希望你能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那些話是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美炎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為了你的那份祈願 能夠賭上靈魂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}如果有不惜接受戰鬥的命運也想要實現的願望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我可以幫助你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}和你結下契約的話 什麼願望都可以實現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}正是如此 你似乎有那樣的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}{\pos(400,326)\fs16\b1}soul gem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你用什麼樣的祈願來讓靈魂寶石發光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我想要將和鹿目同學的相遇重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不是被她所保護的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}而是想要成為保護她的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}契約成立了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}{\pos(400,326)\fs16\b1}entropy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你的願望凌駕了熵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}來 釋放出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你那嶄新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我…還沒有出院
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}來做下自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我叫曉美炎 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美同學因為心臟的疾病一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}鹿目同學 我也成為魔法少女了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}今後一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那麼我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你怎麼看 麻美姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}時間停止呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然確實是很厲害 用法是個問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}麻美姐 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美同學 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}幹的漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好棒啊 小炎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}喂 鹿目同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為什麼…這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}要告訴她們才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}大家都被丘比騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我說啊 丘比撒這種謊會有什麼好處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}想說些奇怪的事來離間我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}難道你其實和那個叫杏子的傢伙不會是一夥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽 那樣才是被離間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不管怎樣 我反對和這女孩組隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小圓和麻美姐用的是遠距離武器所以會沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}突然在眼前爆炸什麼的還是饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}都差點被捲進去好多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美同學沒有炸彈以外的武器了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我稍微考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你這傢伙到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}對小爽做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}求求你 回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這樣的事小爽也應該討厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}抱歉 美樹同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小爽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}可惡 這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}太殘酷了 這太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}巴學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}靈魂寶石會孕育魔女的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}大家不都只有去死了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你也是我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不要 已經受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒事的 我們兩人來加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}一起去打倒魔女之夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我們也到此為止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}{\pos(308,326)\fs16\b1}grief seed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}悲歎之種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}喂 我們倆就這樣變成怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}把這個世界全都搞得一團糟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}討厭的事也好 悲傷的事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}直到全都能當作沒發生過為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}破壞掉 破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不停地破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你不覺得這樣也很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}剛才是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我還留著一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼會 為什麼要給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}因為有一件我做不到小炎卻做得到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎 你能回到過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你說過為了不讓這種結局發生要改變歷史的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你能不能去救救還沒被丘比欺騙的那個笨蛋的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我答應你 絕對會去救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}無論重複多少次 我一定會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}還有一件事可以拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我不想變成魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然有討厭的事也有悲傷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但這個世界上還有許多我想守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎 終於叫我的名字了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好高興…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}誰都 不會相信未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}誰都 無法接受未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那樣的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}誰…是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}即使出現答應給予你奇跡來籠絡你的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}也絕不能聽它擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我不會再依靠任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}也不需要去讓任何人明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}已經不能再讓小圓戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所有的魔女都由我一個人來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}然後這次一定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}由我親手將魔女之夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:59.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつか君が瞳に灯す
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:59.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}曾經你在眼中燃起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:03.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛の光が 時を超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:03.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛的光芒 超越了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:07.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}滅び急ぐ世界の夢を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:07.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}急劇毀滅的世界的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:10.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}確かに一つ 壊すだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:10.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}的確又一個 即將終結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒辦法啊 只有她一個人的話負擔太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.64,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}躊躇いを飲み干して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:13.64,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}飲盡躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼這樣 太過分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:17.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君が望むモノは何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:17.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你所期望的又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}怎麼可以這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:22.37,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}こんな欲深い憧れの行方に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:22.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這樣深重的慾望與憧憬的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:26.41,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}儚い明日はあるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:26.41,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}將是虛幻的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不可以聽那傢伙的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}放棄的話就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如同孩提時代夢見的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}但是 你可以改變命運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:35.69,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}古の魔法のように
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:35.69,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}古老的魔法一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}無法迴避的毀滅與嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:39.57,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闇さえ砕く力で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:39.57,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}用連黑暗也能夠粉碎的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}一切都由你來顛覆即可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你具有的正是為此而生的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:43.40,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}微笑む君に会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:43.40,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要和微笑的你相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:47.23,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怯えるこの手の中には
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:47.23,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}顫抖不止的這雙手中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不要被騙了 那樣就如他所願了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:51.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手折られた花の勇気
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:51.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}緊握著摘下花朵的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}像我這樣的人 真的可以做到些什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.89,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想いだけが頼る全て
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.89,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只有思念是全部的依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}可以改變這樣的結局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:20:01.60,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}光を呼び覚ます願い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:20:01.60,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}是將能夠喚醒光明的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}所以跟我結下契約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}成為魔法少女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不行！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}真的是好厲害啊 變身了的小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}雖然我也預測到她的話是能夠成為最強的魔法少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}沒想到竟然能將那個魔女之夜一擊打倒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}之後的結局會怎樣 你也已經看穿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}無論早晚 結局都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}她作為最強的魔法少女 打倒了最大的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}當然之後也只能成為最邪惡的魔女了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}現在的小圓的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}恐怕只要十天左右就能毀滅這個星球了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不過之後就是你們人類的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我們的能量回收任務也大致已經達成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你不去戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我的戰場不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}曉美炎 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}重複 無論多少次我都將重複
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}無數次輪迴相同的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}尋找唯一的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}尋找把你從絕望的命運中拯救出來的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:21:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我唯一的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}小炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}為了你 如果是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.22,0:22:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}即使我被困在永遠的迷宮中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.41,0:22:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:28.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}交わした約束忘れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:28.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}無法忘記交換過的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:30.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}目を閉じ確かめる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:30.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}而閉上眼睛再次確定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:36.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}押し寄せた闇 振り払って進むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:36.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}驅散聚集的黑暗繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:52.29,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}いつになったらなくした未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:52.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要到什麼時候 失去的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:58.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}私ここでまた見ることできるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:58.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我才能在這裡再次眺望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.67,0:23:03.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}溢れ出した不安の影を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.67,0:23:03.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}無數次撕裂漫溢的不安的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:08.67,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}何度でも裂いてこの世界歩んでこう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:08.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}在這世界上不斷前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:14.36,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}とめどなく刻まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:14.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}打上無盡的刻印的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:19.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}時は今始まり告げ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:19.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}時間此刻宣告著開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:24.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}変わらない思いをのせ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:24.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}乘載著不變的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:30.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}閉ざされた扉開けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:30.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}去打開閉鎖的門扉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:36.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}目覚めた心は走り出した 未来を描くため
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:36.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}甦醒的心為了描繪未來而奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:41.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}難しい道で立ち止まっても空は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:41.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}即使在泥濘的路上停滯不前天空也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:46.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}きれいな青さでいつも待っててくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:46.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}帶著美麗的蔚藍一直等待著我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:48.36,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}だから怖くない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:48.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}所以不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.41,0:23:51.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}もう何があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.41,0:23:51.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:53.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)\fad(200,0)\blur2}第10話    不會再依靠任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:54.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}挫けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:54.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}也不會氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:24:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}在一直看著她們的同時 你就沒有感覺到什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你就沒有想要去理解過 大家有多痛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:09.93,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,220)\blur5}第11話  最後留下的路標

